nodes.text: An individual was a soldier in the Gloom Walkers during the Battle of Phaseera. They were led by Lieutenant Ulabore in an attempt to destroy the Republic outpost on Phaseera, which would allow the Sith army to destroy the Republic's base camp. This soldier shouted out that the mission would result in their deaths when Ulabore told his men their orders. Despite knowing that it would get cause more Gloom Walkers to die, Ulabore refused to listen to Dessel's protests. This angered Dessel, who punched his lieutenant in the jaw, which left Ulabore unconscious and allowed Dessel to command the soldiers.
